              I love to continuously learn and apply my skills into creating various type of projects.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="my-2 mx-2 text-xs italic">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-700"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="xs:text-xs md:text-lg italic font-thin">Web development fascinates me. Keep wondering what is the next cool thing.</div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="my-2 mx-2 text-xs italic">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-700"></i>
                 </div>
                <div class="xs:text-xs md:text-lg italic font-thin">Android development field is another intriguing field.</div></li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="my-2 mx-2 text-xs italic">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-700"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="xs:text-xs md:text-lg italic font-thin">However it all comes together when cyber-security is included in the development process.</div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="my-2 mx-2 text-xs italic">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-700"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="xs:text-xs md:text-lg italic font-thin">I write about what I do and what I find interesting.</div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-8">
            <a class="font-['Roboto'] text-xl text-purple-700 p-2 border-2 border-purple-700 rounded-md hover:bg-purple-700 hover:text-white transition" href="#about">
              Read More ...
            </a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right-side image -->

      <div class="w-auto h-auto z-0 xs:hidden md:block">
        <img class="sm:h-[50%]"
               src="themes/custom/portfolio/assets/images/about.jpeg"
               alt="team_img" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Counts Section -->
    <section class="w-full xs:h-[20vh] lg:h-[20vh] flex xs:p0 justify-center align-center background-image">

      <div class="flex flex-col my-auto items-center">
        <div id="counts" class="sm:text-xl text-4xl text-white p-3 purecounter" data-purecounter-start="0" data-purecounter-end="18" data-purecounter-duration="1">0</div>
        <p class="text-white xs:text-lg lg:text-2xl uppercase">projects</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Skills Section -->
    <section class="w-full xs:min-h-[80vh] md:h-[100vh] lg:h-[80vh] flex flex-col xs:p0 lg:p-6 justify-center align-center bg-gray-200">
      <div class="h-8 uppercase text-2xl align-center my-3 text-purple-700">Skills</div>
      {{ page.skills }}


    </section>
    <!-- Portfolio Section -->
    <section class="portfolio-section"></section>
    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="contact-section"></section>
